WEBVTT

00:00:01.046 --> 00:00:03.744
(In Maori: My mountain is Taupiri.)

00:00:03.744 --> 00:00:06.003
(Waikato is my river.)

00:00:06.048 --> 00:00:08.398
(My name is Marilyn.)

00:00:08.643 --> 00:00:09.833
(Hello.)

00:00:10.728 --> 00:00:13.570
As you've heard, when I was very young,

00:00:13.594 --> 00:00:17.214
I was elected to
the New Zealand Parliament.

00:00:18.496 --> 00:00:23.780
And at that age, you learn mostly
by listening to others' stories.

00:00:25.290 --> 00:00:30.759
I remember a woman
who'd been injured in a farm accident,